    "vuln_description": "The Atavist Magazine website is vulnerable to site-wide CSRF (Cross-Site Request Forgery) attacks due to the absence of CSRF tokens in account settings and subscription cancellation endpoints. This allows an attacker to perform unauthorized actions on behalf of a victim user, such as modifying account settings or canceling subscriptions, without their consent.",
